import React from 'react';
import {
    Nav,
    NavLink,
    Bars,
    NavMenu,
    NavBtn,
    NavBtnLink,
} from './NavbarElements';

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Nav>
                <Bars />

                <NavMenu>
                    <NavLink to='/HomePage' activeStyle>
                        <NavBtn>
                            <NavBtnLink to='/RegisterForm'>RegisterForm</NavBtnLink>
                        </NavBtn>
                        {/* <NavLink to='/RegisterForm' activeStyle>
                        RegisterForm
                    </NavLink> */}
                    </NavLink>

                    {/* <NavLink to='/annual' activeStyle>
                        Annual Report
                    </NavLink>
                    <NavLink to='/team' activeStyle>
                        Teams
                    </NavLink>
                    <NavLink to='/blogs' activeStyle>
                        Blogs
                    </NavLink>
                    <NavLink to='/sign-up' activeStyle>
                        Sign Up
                    </NavLink> */}
                </NavMenu>
                <NavBtn>
                    <NavBtnLink to='/HomePage'>HomePage</NavBtnLink>
                </NavBtn>
            </Nav>
        </>
    );
};

export default Navbar;
